entries.RADIO_PLAYER_NOTE: Shows you the currently playing music title.
entries.CHAT_COMMANDS_NOTE:
Helpful Chat Commands:
A:XX -> Animation
S:XXX -> Snake
M:XXX -> Music
E:XX -> Emotion
I:XXXX -> Item
I:XXXXF:YYYY -> Item with Flag
entries.CHAT_BUTTON_NOTE: Helpful Buttons in the Chat Menu, to copy/paste/delete/send content
entries.SAVE_PLAYER_NO: Player needs to be loaded for this cheat to work!
entries.TOWN_NAME_CHANGER_NOTE: Lets you change your town name, just type in the name you want.
entries.TOWN_NAME_CHANGER_ENTER_NAME: Town Name Changer\n\nEnter the Town Name you'd like to have:

entries.BULL_BOARD_DUMPER_NOTE: Lets you backup and restore your bulletin board mail.
entries.BULLETIN_BOARD_DUMPER_DUMP: Backup your bulletin board message\n\nName the backup you'd like to create.
entries.TREESIZE_NOTE: Lets you change the size of your town tree.
entries.CHANGE_NATIVE_NOTE: Lets you change your native townfruit.
entries.PWP_UNLOCK_NOTE: Lets you unlock/lock every Public Work Project.
entries.GRASS_CHANGER_NOTE: Lets you change your town grass type.
entries.CARAVAN_SET_NOTE: Lets you change the caravans on the campsite.
entries.CAMPING_SET_NOTE: Lets you edit/remove the current villager in your camping ground.
entries.KEY_CHOOSE_UPGRADE: Choose an upgrade for your shop.

entries.QR_MACHINE_NOTE: Lets you unlock/lock the QR Machine.
entries.BUILDING_MOD_NOTE: Lets you place, move, and remove buildings in your town.
entries.FILL_MUSEUM_NOTE: Fills/clears the contents of the museum.
entries.REAL_TIME_ACRE_NOTE: Touch a square on the map to change it's acres. \nWhen you edited the map to your liking, save and close the game. Then, reopen it to get the results.
entries.CANT_PUSH_NOTE: Villagers and players can't push you around.
entries.COORD_MOD_NOTE: Lets you move around your player by changing its coordinates.
entries.MOON_JUMP_NOTE: Press the hotkeys to move your player upwards or downwards.
entries.TOUCH_WARP_NOTE: Touching the map ports your player to the touched position.
entries.WALK_OVER_NOTE: Disables collisions to let you walk over everything.
entries.MOVEMENT_CHANGE_NOTE: Press the hotkeys to set the movement "type" to swimming or walking.
entries.WALK_PARTICLE_CHANGE_NOTE: Lets you change the particles you create while walking. \n
entries.WALK_PARTICLE_CHANGE_ENTER_ID: Type the Particle ID you want to set.
entries.PLAYER_TELEPORT_NOTE: Lets you teleport a selected player to you.
entries.VISIBILITY_MOD_NOTE: Press the hotkeys to change your visibility for other players. You can go fully invisible, or appear as if you're not moving at all.
entries.SPEED_MOD_NOTE: Touch the white keyboard icon to enter a float value for your walking, running and swimming speed.
entries.ROOM_WARPING_NOTE: Press the hotkeys to open up a menu where you can choose a room ID to warp to.
entries.SHOVEL_KNOCKBACK_NOTE: Disables Knockback when hitting rocks or walls with a shovel.
entries.TEXT_2_ITEM_NOTE: Lets you spawn any item you want into your first inventory slot. \n
entries.TEXT_2_ITEM_SET: Enter ID to start the set:
entries.TEXT_2_ITEM_SEARCH_ERR3: No Items found, search for something else!
entries.TEXT_2_ITEM_SEARCH_ERR4: Too many matches! Enter more letters\nMatches: %d
entries.DUPE_ITEMS_NOTE: Lets you duplicate the item from your first inventory slot to the second slot or to all your slots. \n
entries.CATALOG_TO_POCKET_NOTE: Lets you spawn catalog items instantly into your inventory.\n
entries.CHAT_T2I_NOTE: Lets you use your In-Game Chat to spawn in items into your inventory\nJust input the ID into the chat and press the hotkeys, don't send the message.
entries.CLEAR_INV_NOTE: Removes all items from your inventory.
entries.REMOVE_INV_WARNING: Warning\nThis will remove every Item in your Inventory\nPress Yes to proceed or No to Cancel
entries.ITEM_SETTINGS_NOTE: Lets you show off all items/eat all items etc.
entries.SAVE_MENU_CHANGER_NOTE: Lets you change the save menu to a any other menu you want.
entries.SAVE_MENU_CHANGER_ENTER_ID: Type the menu ID you want to load.
entries.GET_SET_NOTE: Lets you spawn custom item sets or preinstalled ones into your inventory.
entries.GET_SET_DUMP: Backup your custom inventory set\n\nName the backup you'd like to create.
entries.CUSTOM_BUTTON_NOTE: Adds buttons to the pop-ups in your inventory.
entries.NAME_CHANGER_NOTE: Lets you change your player name, just type in the name you want + the position.
entries.NAME_CHANGER_ENTER_NAME: Player Name Changer\n\nEnter the Name you'd like to have:
entries.PLAYER_APPEARANCE_NOTE: Lets you modify your eye color/style, hair color/style, gender and your outfit.
entries.RANDOM_PLAYER_NOTE: Randomizes your outfit or your whole player, make sure to backup your player beforehand.
entries.RANDOM_PLAYER_DUMP: Player Backup\n\nName the backup you'd like to create.
entries.TPC_MESSAGE_NOTE: Lets you edit the message in the TPC Menu.
entries.TPC_MESSAGE_ENTER_NAME: TPC Text Changer\n\nEnter the TPC Message you'd like to have:
entries.TPC_SETTINGS_NOTE:
Lets you backup and restore a tpc picture. 
Custom TPC Preferences: 
1. Smaller than 5024 Byte 
2. JPG Picture Format 
3. JPG Dimensions must be 64x104
entries.TPC_DUMPER_NAME: TPC Backup\n\nName the backup you'd like to create.
entries.DESIGN_DUMP_NOTE: Lets you backup and restore your designs.
entries.DESIGN_DUMP_NAME: Design Backup\n\nName the backup you'd like to create.
entries.EMOTION_LIST_NOTE: Lets you fill/clear your emotions + having only one emotion in every slot.
entries.EMOTION_LIST_TYPE_ID: Type the emotion ID you like to have.
entries.DREAM_CODE_NOTE: Lets you change your existing Dream Code.
entries.DREAM_CODE_ENTER_ID: Enter dreamcode: \nInput 4 digits with no spaces 3 times.
entries.DEBUG_MENU_NOTE: Unlocks an unused menu called "Census Menu" into your game where you can see some game stats.
entries.PLAYER_INFO_NOTE: Shows you many informations of your player.
entries.CUSTOM_HAIR_EYE_NOTE: Lets you set custom hair&eye colors for your player! Just input the RGB Value for the new color you want.\nIf you press on "Save" your current custom color will be saved and loaded each time you start the plugin\Note: The custom colors currently only work if you have Hair Color ID 0 and Eye Color ID 1!
entries.CUSTOM_ENTER_HAIR: Enter RGB Color Code for Hair Color:
entries.CUSTOM_ENTER_EYE: Enter RGB Color Code for Eye Color:
entries.WEAR_HELMET_NOTE: Lets you wear a helmet with an accesory at the same time. Make sure the accesory is on first! Thanks to Levi for this cheat.
entries.PLAYER_LOADER_NOTE: Lets you load a specific player of yours without the need to restart the game!
entries.PLAYERS_ON_MAP_NOTE: Shows every loaded player on the map.
entries.NEVER_BEDHEAD_NOTE: Prevents your hair from getting messy when starting the game.
entries.PLAYER_SELECTOR_NOTE: Lets you select other players to be able to put animations and more onto them!.
entries.ANTI_ANIM_NOTE: Will stop others from executing animations on you.
entries.ANIMATION_MOD_NOTE: Lets you execute animations onto you or others.
entries.ANIMATIONS_ANIM_NOTE: Lets you set animations onto you or others\nEnter Animation ID:.
entries.ANIMATIONS_TOOL_NOTE: Lets you set tools onto you or others\nEnter Tool ID:.
entries.ANIMATIONS_SNAKE_NOTE: Lets you set snake animations onto you or others\nEnter Snake ID:.
entries.ANIMATIONS_EMOTE_NOTE: Lets you set emote animations onto you or others\nEnter Emotion ID:.
entries.ANIMATIONS_SOUND_NOTE: Lets you set sound or music\nEnter Sound/Music ID:.
entries.ANIMATIONS_APPEAR_NOTE1: Lets you edit yours or others appearance\nEnter Hairsytle ID:.
entries.ANIMATIONS_APPEAR_NOTE2: Lets you edit yours or others appearance\nEnter Haircolor ID:.
entries.ANIMATIONS_APPEAR_NOTE3: Lets you edit yours or others appearance\nEnter Eyecolor ID:.
entries.EMOTION_LOOP_NOTE: Lets you loop a selected emotion.\n
entries.IDLE_NOTE: Press the hotkeys to idle your player which will reset your players animation.
entries.SLOW_MO_ANIM_NOTE: Makes animations look slower to get a nice effect.
entries.ANIM_ON_ALL_NOTE: This sets an Animation on every player at once. This does set the Game Mode to online mode to prevent issues when playing online.
entries.PICK_SEEDER_NOTE: Lets you pickup and seed items with many different modes.
entries.WALK_SEEDER_NOTE: Lets you remove items while walking over them.
entries.FIREWORK_SEEDER_NOTE: Lets you edit the item that gets spawned when you drop a firework.
entries.FIREWORK_SEEDER_ENTER_ID: Type the item ID you'd like to seed.
entries.MAP_EDITOR_NOTE: Lets you drop items in a more precised way to decorate your town or island for example.
entries.ALL_SEEDER_NOTE: Lets you change every item you pickup/drop or in any other way interact through the player!\nYou need to hold down the Hotkey to use the cheat!
entries.ITEM_SEQUENCER_NOTE:
This lets you drop items in a patterns with any dropper cheat
Example:
First Item is 335B (Golden Shovel)
Second Item is 0070 (Bell Tree)
The example will now drop a shovel then a tree and then again a shovel, etc...
entries.ITEM_SEQUENCER_ENTER_ID: Enter new Item ID:\n(B to remove)
entries.DROP_MODS_NOTE: Settings for the different dropper cheats.
entries.DROP_MODS_ENTER_ID: Enter ID to replace\n(0xFFFFFFFF to replace everything)
entries.DROP_ITEMS_NOTE: Lets you drop items instantly without the need of going into the inventory.
entries.AUTO_DROP_NOTE: Lets you drop items automatically in a 3x3 radius (can be changed with the Drop Modifier cheat).
entries.TOUCH_DROP_NOTE: Touch the screen to drop an item at the touched position.
entries.SLOT_DROP_NOTE: Lets you drop the item you selected in your inventory.
entries.INF_FRUIT_TREE_NOTE: Fruits will drop infinitely from fruit trees.
entries.AXE_TREE_SHAKE_NOTE: Shaking trees chops them down as if you're using an axe.
entries.FRUIT_TREE_MOD_NOTE: Changes all fruits on fruit trees to the entered item ID.
entries.INST_TREE_CHOP_NOTE: Trees chop down with one hit.
entries.WALLET_NOTE: Spawns the entered amount of bells into your wallet.
entries.BANK_NOTE: Spawns the entered amount of bells into your bank.
entries.MEOW_COUPONS_NOTE: Spawns a entered amount of meow coupons.
entries.BADGES_NOTE: Spawns all bronze/silver/gold badges into your badge list.
entries.MEDALS_NOTE: Spawns a entered amount of medals.
entries.TURNIPS_NOTE: Changes the turnip prices for the current week.
entries.UNLOCK_ISLAND_NOTE: Lets you unlock/lock access to the island and club tortimer.
entries.FILL_INV_ORE_NOTE: Makes the game think you have a inventory filled with the bonus ore, therefore receiving max points at the tour results.
entries.FILL_INV_FRUIT_NOTE: Makes the game think you already have all the needed fruits for the tour to finish.
entries.FREE_KAPPN_NOTE: Lets you go to the island without the need of paying or having money at all.
entries.ISLAND_SHOP_MOD_NOTE: Lets you change the items displayed in the island shop.
entries.ISLAND_SHOP_MOD_ENTER_ID: Type an ID for Item Slot %d.
entries.ALL_TOURS_NOTE: Unlocks all the island tours for your current island session.
entries.ISLAND_ACRE_NOTE: Touch the white keyboard icon to open up a keyboard to enter 16 acre IDs. Acres are counted left to right, top to bottom. Enable this cheat before you arrive on a new island. Only works as host.
entries.ISLAND_BUILDING_NOTE: Touch the white keyboard icon to enter building data for the 2 island buildings. Enable this cheat before you arrive on a new island. Only works as host.
entries.ISLAND_SAVER_NO: You need to be on the island for this cheat to work!
entries.ISLAND_SAVER_DUMPER_DUMP: Island Saver\n\nName the backup you'd like to create.
entries.NPC_SELECTOR_NOTE: Lets you select any loaded NPC to be able to use the other NPC Cheats.
entries.NPC_ANIMATION_NOTE: Lets you set animations onto selected NPC's. First set the animation ID by clicking the keyboard and then execute it by pressing the hotkeys.
entries.NPC_COORDINATE_NOTE: Lets you move around selected NPC's.
entries.NPC_TELEPORT_NOTE: Lets you teleport selected NPC's to your location.
entries.SIZE_CODES_NOTE: Lets you customize sizes of players, npcs, bugs, etc...
entries.T_POSE_NOTE: Lets you reset player/NPC position to a T-Pose.
entries.TAKE_TPC_PIC_NOTE: Lets you take TPC Pictures anywhere instantly. Just press the hotkeys to Take the picture, you can also freeze the screen to make sure your shot looks good.
entries.MAX_TURBO_NOTE: This spams everything that is activated with A,B,X,Y and DPadUp, -Left, -Down and -Right.
entries.MULTI_PRESS_NOTE: Lets you multi press tools and many other things.
entries.ULTIMATE_POPPER_NOTE: Modifies the Party Popper to be able to spam it.\nTo edit the particle ID press the hotkeys.
entries.CAMERA_MOD_NOTE:
Lets you move around your camera freely
R + CPad Lets you rotate the camera
R + X Lets you stop the camera from following you
R + Y Lets you lock your player
B + DPad Lets you move around the camera
entries.FISH_ALWAYS_BITE_NOTE: Fish will always bite right away.
entries.FISH_CANT_SCARE_NOTE: Fish will not be scared by the player running.
entries.CHAT_DONT_DISSAPEAR_NOTE: Chat bubbles will stay on screen until a new message was sent.
entries.CHATCOPYPASTE_NOTE: Lets you copy and paste your chat. Copied content will be saved to a clipboard on your sdcard.
entries.FORCE_CHAT_NOTE: Forces the chat to be automatically sent.
entries.SHOP_ALWAYS_OPEN_NOTE: Lets you remove the closing times of shops so they always stay open.
entries.DISABLE_SAVE_NOTE: Disables save menus which are opened by pressing the START button.
entries.DISABLE_ITEM_LOCKS_NOTE: Removes the "delay-lock" of dropping. This lets you drop items faster.
entries.CANT_FALL_HOLE: Can't Fall In Holes Or Pitfalls
entries.CANT_FALL_HOLE_NOTE: Makes holes and pitfalls non functional so you won't fall into them.
entries.SET_SPOT_STATE_NOTE: Locks/unlocks the map or only spot where you are standing.
entries.SEARCH_REPLACE_NOTE: Lets you replace all instances of a searched item on the map with a different item.\n(Search for 0xFFFFFFFF to replace everything)
entries.QUICK_MENU_SEARCH_REPLACE_SEARCH: Enter the ID of the item you\nwould like to search\n(0xFFFFFFFF to replace everything):
entries.QUICK_MENU_SEARCH_REPLACE_REPLACE: Enter the ID of the item you\nwould like to place:
entries.REMOVE_MAP_ITEMS_NOTE: Lets you remove all items from the map.
entries.REMOVE_ITEM_WARNING: Warning\nThis will remove every Item on your Map\nPress Yes to proceed or No to Cancel
entries.WATER_FLOWERS_NOTE: This will water all your flowers in town/on island.
entries.WEED_REMOVER_NOTE: Lets you remove all weeds in your town/on your island.
entries.WEED_REMOVER_KEY:
Select Mode:
-Offline will remove every weed in an 
instant(but will crash the connection if playing online!)
Online Mode will remove 800 Weeds in every second(will not crash the online 
connection)
entries.EDIT_PATTERN_NOTE: Edits the ownership of every pattern you have to be yours so you can edit them.
entries.GRASS_EDITOR_NOTE: Lets you clear/fill grass at the player's position. Also lets you clear/fill all grass on the map at once.
entries.GRASS_EDITOR_KB1: What do you want to do?
entries.AMIIBO_SPOOFER_NOTE: Lets you spawn every amiibo at every location. Huge thanks to Slattz for creating this cheat!
entries.TIME_TRAVEL_NOTE: Lets you freely move the time forward/backward. Also lets you go forward/backward a specific time!
entries.TIME_ERROR: Error: %d is the highest amount for %s!
entries.BURIED_INSPECTOR_NOTE: Lets you dig up items by picking them up by hand.
entries.TOOL_ANIM_NOTE: Changes the effects from every tool to a custom animation ID.
entries.GAME_TYPE_NOTE: This let's you change the gametype you are currently in. As an example set it to online 2 to be able to send friend requests to others on the online islands.
entries.WEATHER_MOD_NOTE: Lets you change the current weather.
entries.ALWAYS_AURORA_MOD_NOTE: Will make aurora lights always appear no matter the time or date!
entries.MORE_NUMBERS_NOTE: Lets you type in more than 3 numbers on the online island.
entries.LARGE_FOV_NOTE: Gives you a larger FOV to see more.
entries.MOVE_FURN_NOTE: This lets you move around any Furniture in any Building (works online).
entries.WALK_TALK_NOTE: Lets you move around while talking to npcs, reading signs, etc...
entries.KEY_EXTEND_NOTE: Removes the keylimit for the keyboard.
entries.CUSTOM_KEY_NOTE: Gives you custom symbols for your keyboard.
entries.BEANS_PARTICLE_NOTE: Lets you change the particles spawned by the beans.\n
entries.DAYTIME_NOTE: Sets a daytime filter onto your game which makes the game much brighter at night.
entries.FAST_MODE_NOTE: Functions are executed twice as fast.\n
entries.FAST_TEXT_SPEED_NOTE: Lets you speed up text boxes.
entries.FAST_GAME_SPEED_NOTE: Lets you speed up the game.
entries.FAST_ISABELLE_NOTE: Enables fast text speed and fast game speed while in the greeting room
entries.RESTORE_NOFILES: Error\nCouldn't find any files to restore.
entries.FILE_PROMPT: Do you really want to delete %s?
entries.FILE_RES2: Error\nCouldn't find any files to delete.
